import React, { useState } from 'react'; import { Box, Typography, Grid, Card, Paper, Button, List, ListItem, ListItemIcon, ListItemText, Chip, LinearProgress, Dialog, DialogTitle, DialogContent, DialogActions, Table, TableBody, TableCell, TableContainer, TableHead, TableRow, Avatar, Stepper, Step, StepLabel, StepContent } from '@mui/material'; import { Add, School, Schedule, Warning, TrendingUp, People, Group, Class, CalendarToday, BarChart, Cloud, Storage, Wifi, Security, CheckCircle, Error, Info, Notifications, Download, Refresh, AutoAwesome } from '@mui/icons-material'; const OverviewTab = ({ advancedStats, systemHealthStats, systemStats, notifications, recentActivities, onAddUser, onGenerateTimetable, onStatClick }) => { const [performanceDialog, setPerformanceDialog] = useState(false); const [selectedPerformance, setSelectedPerformance] = useState(null); // Performance metrics data const performanceMetrics = [ { metric: 'System Response Time', value: 128, unit: 'ms', target: 200, status: 'excellent' }, { metric: 'Database Queries', value: 2450, unit: 'qps', target: 3000, status: 'good' }, { metric: 'API Success Rate', value: 99.8, unit: '%', target: 99.5, status: 'excellent' }, { metric: 'Server CPU Usage', value: 45, unit: '%', target: 80, status: 'good' }, { metric: 'Memory Usage', value: 62, unit: '%', target: 85, status: 'good' }, { metric: 'Network Latency', value: 18, unit: 'ms', target: 50, status: 'excellent' } ]; const upcomingEvents = [ { id: 1, title: 'Faculty Meeting', date: '2024-01-15', time: '10:00 AM', type: 'meeting' }, { id: 2, title: 'Mid-term Exams', date: '2024-01-20', type: 'academic' }, { id: 3, title: 'System Maintenance', date: '2024-01-25', time: '2:00 AM', type: 'maintenance' }, { id: 4, title: 'New Semester Starts', date: '2024-02-01', type: 'academic' } ]; const handlePerformanceClick = (metric) => { setSelectedPerformance(metric); setPerformanceDialog(true); }; const getPerformanceColor = (status) => { switch (status) { case 'excellent': return 'success'; case 'good': return 'primary'; case 'warning': return 'warning'; case 'critical': return 'error'; default: return 'default'; } }; const getEventColor = (type) => { switch (type) { case 'meeting': return 'primary'; case 'academic': return 'secondary'; case 'maintenance': return 'warning'; default: return 'default'; } }; const PerformanceDetailsDialog = ({ open, onClose, metric }) => { if (!metric) return null; return ( Performance Details - {metric.metric} {metric.value} {metric.unit} Current Value Target: {metric.target} {metric.unit} Status Analysis ); }; return ( {/* Header Section */} 📊 System Overview {/* Advanced Stats Cards */} {advancedStats.map((stat, index) => ( onStatClick(stat)} > {stat.icon} {stat.value} {stat.label} {stat.change} {stat.description} Click for details → ))} {/* Main Content Column */} {/* Quick Actions */} 🚀 Quick Actions {/* System Health */} 🏥 System Health {systemHealthStats.map((stat, index) => ( {stat.icon} {stat.label} {stat.value} {stat.description && `• ${stat.description}`} ))} {/* Performance Metrics */} 📈 Performance Metrics Metric Value Target Status Progress {performanceMetrics.map((metric, index) => ( handlePerformanceClick(metric)} > {metric.metric} {metric.value} {metric.unit} {metric.target} {metric.unit} ))}
{/* Horizontal Cards Section */} {/* Notifications */} 🔔 Notifications !n.read).length} color="error" size="small" /> {notifications.slice(0, 4).map((notification) => ( {notification.type === 'warning' && } {notification.type === 'error' && } {notification.type === 'success' && } {notification.type === 'info' && } {!notification.read && ( )} ))} {notifications.length > 4 && ( )} {/* Recent Activities */} 📈 Recent Activities {recentActivities.map((activity) => ( {activity.icon} ))} {/* Upcoming Events */} 📅 Upcoming Events {upcomingEvents.map((event) => ( ))} {/* System Status Stepper */} System Status Database Connection Connected to primary database cluster API Services All microservices running normally Security Systems Firewall and security protocols active {/* Performance Details Dialog */} setPerformanceDialog(false)} metric={selectedPerformance} /> ); }; export default OverviewTab;
